Reverse Image Search Using Yandex & TinEye
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Perform manual reverse image searches using Yandex, Bing, and TinEye
Understand differences between reverse image search platforms
Develop Python automation scripts for reverse image searching
Analyze and compare results across multiple platforms
Apply reverse image search techniques for OSINT investigations
Prerequisites
Basic Linux command line knowledge
Python programming fundamentals (functions, loops, file I/O)
Understanding of HTTP requests and web scraping concepts
Familiarity with JSON data format
